tags.name: Agent
tags.description: An Agent is an Organisation that acts on behalf of a Learner to assist with Enrolments.

tags.name: Assessor
tags.description: An Assessor is a Staff record that has Assessor Flag enabled. Used in Course Offer, Unit Offer, Course Enrolment and Unit Enrolment.

tags.name: AuditLog
tags.description: An AuditLog is a record that has information about actions on entities such as insert, update and delete events.

tags.name: Checklist
tags.description: Checklists can be added to all record types to collect additional data unique to your Education Provider's requirements.

tags.name: ChecklistItem
tags.description: A Checklist Item is the available list of Checklists. Used in Checklists.

tags.name: Coordinator
tags.description: A Coordinator is a Staff record that has Coordinator Flag enabled. Used in Course, Course Offer and Course Enrolment.

tags.name: Course
tags.description: A Course is used to outline the certification being awarded.

tags.name: CourseEnrolment
tags.description: A Course Enrolment is the relationship between a Learner and a Course Offer.

tags.name: CourseOffer
tags.description: A Course Offer is an instance of a Course that is configured for specific delivery requirements (Locations, Dates, Funding). A Learner is added as a Course Enrolment against a Course Offer.

tags.name: Credential
tags.description: Credentials refer to Certificates, Statements of Attainment etc. They are linked to Course Enrolments

tags.name: DocumentFile
tags.description: A DocumentFile provides a link to upload and download files.

tags.name: Entity
tags.description: Entities are how Wisenet categorises its sections. They are used in other endpoints to define relationships between one Entity and another, e.g. File Notes or Audit Logs.

tags.name: ElementEnrolment
tags.description: An Element Enrolment is the relationship between a UnitEnrolment and an Element.

tags.name: Filenote
tags.description: A Filenote allows notes and documents to be stored against a record.

tags.name: Invoice
tags.description: Invoices contain Invoice, LineItems and Payments information and is linked to a Learner.

tags.name: LanguageLiteracyNumeracy
tags.description: Tracks Language Literacy Numeracy information and is linked to a Course Enrolment

tags.name: LearnerAu
tags.description: This is the Australian version of the Learner endpoint. It contains AU specific fields and logic.

tags.name: LearnerNz
tags.description: This is the New Zealand version of the Learner endpoint. It contains NZ specific fields and logic.

tags.name: LearnerSa
tags.description: This is the South Africa version of the Learner endpoint. It contains SA specific fields and logic.

tags.name: LearnerSg
tags.description: This is the Singapore version of the Learner endpoint. It contains SG specific fields and logic.

tags.name: LearnerPosition
tags.description: A Learner Position is the relationship between a Learner and a Workplace.

tags.name: Location
tags.description: A Location is used to define the site of delivery. It can be linked with Course Offer, Unit Offer and Unit Enrolment.

tags.name: Opportunity
tags.description: An Opportunity tracks a sales deal linked against a Sales Contact.

tags.name: Promotion
tags.description: A Promotion is a specific sales campaign that is available to Agents.

tags.name: SalesContact
tags.description: A Sales Contact is any person who has a relationship with the education provider.

tags.name: SalesPerson
tags.description: A Sales Person is a Staff record that has Assessor Flag enabled. Used in Course Enrolment and Sales.

tags.name: Staff
tags.description: Used to record any Staff member within the training organisation.

tags.name: Tag
tags.description: Tags work like keywords that can be associated with records to group similar records.

tags.name: Trainer
tags.description: A Trainer is a Staff record that has Assessor Flag enabled. Used in Course Offer, Unit Offer, Course Enrolment and Unit Enrolment.

tags.name: Unit
tags.description: A Unit is used to record individual subjects or modules that are required for a Course.

tags.name: UnitOffer
tags.description: A Unit Offer is an instance of a Unit that belongs to a Course Offer and is configured for specific delivery requirements (Locations, Dates, Funding). A Learner is added as a Unit Enrolment against a Unit Offer.

tags.name: UnitEnrolment
tags.description: A Unit Enrolment is the relationship between a Course Enrolment and an Unit Offer.

tags.name: USI
tags.description: Allows a USI record to be verified against the USI service.

tags.name: Workplace
tags.description: Workplaces can be used for tracking details for any type of employment or training based organisation.

tags.name: Combo
tags.description: A combo is also known as a dropdown in Wisenet. Each combo returns the available records with the required Id that is needed when interacting with the non-combo endpoints.
